ing: 1 (3 ounce) package dried Golden Delicious apples
des: "An excellent summer salad that can be altered to suit your liking. Other cheeses I have used include Cheddar and blue cheese. I have also added grilled chicken breast to make it a dinner salad."
ins: In a large bowl, mix the romaine lettuce, strawberries, feta cheese, dried cranberries, dried apples, and pine nuts. Toss with the raspberry vinaigrette salad dressing to serve.
